{"tid":1477524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"七百幾位被捕人士中，有幾多人已被毆打至遍體麟傷？","createTime":"2019-08-16T07:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T07:43:46.000Z","uid":53000,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"78247fed750ccfbfaa67bf11f13bea08f93487e0","tid":1477524,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:03:55.000Z","msg":"以前警察會用電話簿加鎚仔打<br />\n確保冇明顯傷痕<br />\n<br />\n但依家係光明正大咁打<br />\n仲狼死過朱經緯同七警<br />\n好多人被捕後被打至腦出血，<br />\n骨折，頸椎移位，失禁<br />\n<br />\n大家記得警署內的 Lan 線自殺事件嗎？<br />\n你相信警方嗎？<br />\n定還是被毆打至死，然後被自殺？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我懇請大家提供相片廣傳<br />\n香港仍然有好多人縱有雙目但看不到<br />\n有很多人不知道這事<br />\n以為被捕人士只要冇做過就可以喺法庭得到公平審訊，<br />\n七百位被捕人士，分分鐘已經在瀕死邊緣，<br />\n然後他們的名字會被忘記，甚至是沒有名字的 no body<br />\n<br />\n然而殺人者卻逍遙自在"},{"pid":"e62882ce2c2429edf9a31a8c35a129893e1b8ce0","tid":1477524,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:05:42.000Z","msg":"816<br />\n818"},{"pid":"521b8231016c48e6fbd9db8cee9a7dc1ae8d311c","tid":1477524,"uid":182774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:07:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"888aafb5e8c7b7d41def91ab430b1dd99b6819e4","tid":1477524,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:07:45.000Z","msg":"唔出得post講，想知都冇得知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44374a036c76da9d9662166613f6cdf82bb5716c","tid":1477524,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:08:08.000Z","msg":"仲有無數人好彩避過現場追捕，但飽經神經毒氣同警暴武力對待但唔敢求醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f17522f5b67392a55d85909dc37bf94f38f9f0d","tid":1477524,"uid":15626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"521b8231016c48e6fbd9db8cee9a7dc1ae8d311c","tid":1477524,"uid":182774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:07:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:14:00.000Z","msg":"好似習慣左咁<img src=\"/